{"tid":1044400,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［倚天屠龍記]大陸版殷素素 - 陳欣予","createTime":"2019-03-03T00:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T10:30:18.000Z","uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"235729cb05bca7277766f2cbd77da13a04b183dd","tid":1044400,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:33:47.000Z","msg":"《倚天屠龍記》已經第8次被拍成電視劇，而今次的內地版本，由曾執導新版《射鵰英雄傳》的蔣家駿操刀，而上次捧紅了年青演員楊旭文及李一桐，有過成功例子，在新《倚天》亦主攻小鮮肉，尤其一班主要女角，更通通是年青美女，其中演出殷素素的陳欣予，更是只得27歲的90後，曾演出過《幻城》及《泡沫之夏》，但陳欣予要演活這個亦正亦邪的角色，看來是有點稚嫩，未必令人信服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/083329_909127874198edffc94a2d10492bf8b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F083329_909127874198edffc94a2d10492bf8b6.png&h=a8462880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/083329_519a476db8d9b150c404f2c93642b62c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F083329_519a476db8d9b150c404f2c93642b62c.png&h=be2073df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/083330_79cae0825aace74c1556255f81909c04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F083330_79cae0825aace74c1556255f81909c04.png&h=26e4b358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/083331_959db5f568b60614150d7b637f1419e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F083331_959db5f568b60614150d7b637f1419e0.png&h=54b809ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c89d65fcca21f848603f807792e6909c6d7e44ad","tid":1044400,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:40:35.000Z","msg":"拍完又拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2cbc482eee98477ba1330126968a58a4f25731","tid":1044400,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33524f64cfc73a02dbe006cca3bb538b6b52593b","tid":1044400,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/085507_3f62773d49514aa1aea5c97b80979b2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F085507_3f62773d49514aa1aea5c97b80979b2b.png&h=46b24674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/085507_68b08df6cef45238c61052af48be806a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F085507_68b08df6cef45238c61052af48be806a.png&h=ec7f8ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/085508_fedef9f48f56f9e7fe02717b96703f4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F085508_fedef9f48f56f9e7fe02717b96703f4c.png&h=5913cbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/085508_0a84601a261ad92357221d1d94ee3a6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F085508_0a84601a261ad92357221d1d94ee3a6b.png&h=07f33bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/085509_84163503f4ca86bcb3fff19923178780.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F085509_84163503f4ca86bcb3fff19923178780.png&h=591ef717&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37434d789d66d0aaafbdcae85abf8b80b2b89f3a","tid":1044400,"uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:58:20.000Z","msg":"最近新版《倚天屠龍記》開播，劇中女演員顏值都很高，除趙敏、周芷若等扮演者顏值超高外，其中張無忌母親殷素素扮演者也驚艷網友，被讚太美了。其實殷素素一出場的時候，就驚艷了很多網友。已經有越來越多的網友紛紛留言，紛紛稱讚殷素素顏值太美了。<br />\n<br />\n其實，陳欣予本身就長得甜美可人俘獲了很多的觀眾，此前，她在玄幻劇《幻城》中扮演的潮涯，給人印象深刻，而且她那清新靈動的裝扮更是得到觀眾的肯定；在諜戰劇《破陣》里，她飾演的何雲音頗受肯定，她的表現不僅受到了導演的好評。<br />\n<br />\n陳欣予不但長得好看，還是一個高學歷的學霸，她畢業於名牌大學，是復旦大學的上海視覺藝術學院畢業生，學的是美術專業。中國內地演員、模特。陳欣予在拍戲之前，曾挑戰許多極限運動和競技遊戲的比賽項目，獲得過非常好的成績。<br />\n<br />\n陳欣予扮演的殷素素確實很驚艷，圈粉也是自然的，據悉她還先後出演過《蘭陵王》、《大當家》、《千金女賊》、《何以笙簫默》等電視劇作品。陳欣予從小就熱愛表演，只不過父親反對她最終去復旦大學學了美術專業。後來她在大學時期她認識了一個演藝經紀人，從此開啟了自己的演藝之路。<br />\n<br />\n陳欣予雖然名氣不大，但是很努力。因為喜歡所以投入，所以能出好成績。陳欣予飾演的殷素素獲得了超高的評價。她擁有好看的顏值、不錯的演技，看來這次要火了。"},{"pid":"b80730e71270254f603403bf56ccb41a05da37d8","tid":1044400,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"原來先27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee94c559175a13c9d83d59d7791a4e637415ab43","tid":1044400,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"Fuckable"},{"pid":"7677da40c6c1699fda247c989e04de86c2ad7860","tid":1044400,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"大陸西，不了，合港蝗囗味"},{"pid":"3770f75557713b6605b8c6ff13c73d5bc37ce666","tid":1044400,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/143515_1bd56e88e950ecd7afb60a8cdab6fa22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F143515_1bd56e88e950ecd7afb60a8cdab6fa22.png&h=34eb74c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/143516_a07dcec509765f0952d34a9c2a891da0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F143516_a07dcec509765f0952d34a9c2a891da0.png&h=ff2f8a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/143517_c0afa37bca843ac4071b87b9f92af930.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?